performanceLogDetail

Summary
A log for performance metrics. We track a number of performance metrics on the active system. This is primarily used as a tool in production to identify hotspots that may require tuning and optimization. Some care needs to be taken to avoid enabling so many metrics that the performance logging itself becomes a bottleneck.
